OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to life after
OL,4,Cstabbing stranger to death
OL,6,FA 17-year-old boy from Nuneaton has
OL,7,Fbeen sentenced to life with a minimum
OL,8,Fterm of 13 years and three months on
OL,9,Fcharges of murder and possession of a
OL,10,Fknife in public.
OL,12,FThe boy, who cannot be named for legal
OL,13,Freasons, was sentenced at Warwick
OL,14,FCrown Court on 20 September.
OL,16,FIt's after 25-year-old Tom Ellis was
OL,17,Fstabbed whilst out celebrating his
OL,18,Fbirthday on 8 June on Queens Road in
OL,19,FNuneaton.
