OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to life after
OL,4,Cstabbing stranger to death
OL,6,FTom had been on his way to a pub with
OL,7,Fhis partner and family for a final
OL,8,Fdrink following a day out in
OL,9,FBirmingham.
OL,11,FThe group passed by a group of four
OL,12,Fteenage boys.
OL,14,FTown centre CCTV footage from the
OL,15,Fnight shows that there was a brief
OL,16,Fexchange of words between Tom and the
OL,17,Fboys, the offender twice choosing to
OL,18,Fgo after Tom.
