OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to life after
OL,4,Cstabbing stranger to death
OL,6,FA member of Tom's group attempted to
OL,7,Fdeescalate the situation, placing
OL,8,Fherself between Tom and the 17-year-
OL,9,Fold (16 at the time), who was
OL,10,Fpreparing to produce a knife from his
OL,11,Fwaistband.
OL,13,FTom was then stabbed in the chest.
OL,15,FThe group of four ran off down
OL,16,FStratford Street, chased by members of
OL,17,FTom's party.
