OL,4,Cstabbing stranger to death
OL,6,FThe teenager who stabbed Tom had
OL,7,Fposted an image of the weapon taken on
OL,8,Fthe floor of a toilet at Nuneaton's
OL,9,FAsda store onto social media just
OL,10,Fhours before.
OL,12,FA relative of the offender said the
OL,13,Fboy had been behaving strangely after
OL,14,Fthe incident, including leaving a
OL,15,Fbottle of bleach-based cleaning
OL,16,Fproduct out (when ordinarily he did
OL,17,Fnot clean anything) and being evasive
OL,18,Fwhen approached about it.
