OL,6,FTom's partner Alexis said "Tom gave me
OL,7,Fthe best memories of my life, the day
OL,8,Fhe left the world felt a little darker.
OL,10,F"Tom's big smile, laughter and
OL,11,Fcompassion will always be missing from
OL,12,Four lives, but we will always love our
OL,13,FViking."
OL,15,FTom's dad Chris said "We'd like to
OL,16,Fthank the police for everything
OL,17,Fthey've done as part of this
OL,18,Finvestigation and all the support that
OL,19,Fthey've given to us"
