OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to life after
OL,4,Cstabbing stranger to death
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Gareth Unett of
OL,7,Fthe Major Investigations Unit said
OL,8,F"This was a tragedy involving two
OL,9,Fcomplete strangers meeting at random,
OL,10,Fleading to one of them losing his life
OL,11,Fin a senseless act of violence.
OL,13,F"I would like to thank the officers
OL,14,Fand staff who have worked long hours
OL,15,Fto resolve this investigation, and to
OL,16,Fthe local businesses who were helpful
OL,17,Fand supportive in helping us gather
OL,18,Ffootage and evidence.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
