OL,6,F"Most of all to the family of Tom who
OL,7,Fhave acted with absolute dignity
OL,8,Fduring this investigation, I am
OL,9,Fgrateful for their trust, and our
OL,10,Fthoughts remain with them.
OL,12,F'It's important I also acknowledge the
OL,13,Fcourage of those who were present at
OL,14,Fthe time of the incident.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
