OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to life after
OL,4,Cstabbing stranger to death
OL,6,F"They had to relive the event during
OL,7,Fthe preparation of their witness
OL,8,Ftestimonies and will carry those
OL,9,Fmemories for the rest of their lives.
OL,10,FThe investigation team remain thankful
OL,11,Fto them for having the courage and
OL,12,Fstrength to give their accounts.
OL,14,F"Tom was clearly a kind, gentle, and
OL,15,Fmuch-loved individual. No sentence
OL,16,Fwill bring him back, but I hope our
OL,17,Finvestigation is able to provide some
OL,18,Fanswers to Tom's loved ones.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
