OL,3,CTeenager sentenced to life after
OL,4,Cstabbing stranger to death
OL,6,F"Warwickshire Police and our
OL,7,Fcommunities will not tolerate people
OL,8,Fcarrying knives. We continue to work
OL,9,Fwith partners to educate and divert
OL,10,Fpeople away from knife crime. Where
OL,11,Findividuals carry knives or offend
OL,12,Fwith knifes, we will seek to place
OL,13,Fthem before the courts.
OL,15,F"It is vital you tell us if you think
OL,16,Fthat someone is carrying a knife. It's
OL,17,Ftoo late to save Tom, but you might
OL,18,Fsave someone else."
